==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rooter
<hw>Rooter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who, or
that which, roots; one that tears up by the roots.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who roots, or applauds.</def> <mark>[Slang, U.
S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rootery</ent>⟦br⟧
